highlights.text: “You’re Losing Me (From The Vault)” by Taylor Swift is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #26.
“Let It Snow! Let It Snow! Let It Snow! (with The B. Swanson Quartet)” by Frank Sinatra and B. Swanson Quartet is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 135 spots at #49.
Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “Is It Over Now? (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)” is the highest at #14.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 184 weeks straight.
